// ### StatSpecialize ###
//	MaxStatValue: Max value of Stat Option value to set when there is no criteria met for any of steps, see explanation below
//
// ### StatSpecialize::Class ###
//	ID: Defines character base class type
//		~ 1: Dark Wizard
//		~ 2: Dark Knight
//		~ 3: Fairy Elf
//		~ 4: Magic Gladiator
//		~ 5: Dark Lord
